Package: heatcal
Type: Package
Title: Calendar Heatmap Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lars", "Bernhardsson", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cran.sherry228@passinbox.com"))
Description: Create calendar heatmap visualizations for time-series data.
    Each day is displayed as a colored cell, with colors representing values.
    Supports multiple color schemes, Monday or Sunday week starts, and
    automatically handles multi-year data.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/lab1702/heatcal
BugReports: https://github.com/lab1702/heatcal/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    grDevices,
    graphics
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    roxygen2,
    devtools
Config/testthat/edition: 3
